      <p>No elevators. No stairs. Just a single-story neighborhood where every amenity is a short, pleasant walk from your front door.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="amenities-grid">
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal"><div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('home', 22) }}</div><div><h4>Single-Story Campus</h4><p>Accessible, walkable, and easy to navigate for residents and visitors alike.</p></div></div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal"><div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('leaf', 22) }}</div><div><h4>Landscaped Gardens</h4><p>Walking paths, seasonal blooms, and a resident communal garden to plant your own favorites.</p></div></div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal"><div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('flower', 22) }}</div><div><h4>Screened Porch</h4><p>A large covered porch overlooking the courtyard. One of the favorite gathering spots on campus.</p></div></div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal"><div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('book', 22) }}</div><div><h4>Library &amp; Computer Room</h4><p>Quiet corners for reading, writing, and staying connected online.</p></div></div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal"><div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('users', 22) }}</div><div><h4>Private Event Rooms</h4><p>Perfect for family birthdays, holidays, and special occasions.</p></div></div>
