    </div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-card__media"><img src="{{ images.wellnessPool }}" alt="Heated indoor saltwater pool" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="feature-card__body">
          <h3>Heated Saltwater Pool</h3>
          <p>Indoor, year-round, and gentle on joints. Water aerobics, lap swimming, and guided classes throughout the week.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-card__media"><img src="{{ images.wellnessFitness }}" alt="Fitness class for seniors" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="feature-card__body">
          <h3>Fitness &amp; Strength</h3>
          <p>Senior-friendly equipment, balance training, and one-on-one sessions with our licensed trainer.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-card__media"><img src="{{ images.wellnessYoga }}" alt="Gentle yoga session" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="feature-card__body">
          <h3>Mind &amp; Spirit</h3>
          <p>Gentle yoga, meditation, music, and arts programs designed to engage every part of a life well lived.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
