        <h3>Chef-led, resident-driven.</h3>
        <p>Our culinary team plans menus around what residents actually want to eat: classic Southern favorites, lighter fare, and holiday specialties throughout the year. Dietary needs are accommodated with care, and requests are always welcome.</p>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li>Three meals daily</li>
          <li>Restaurant-style service</li>
          <li>Dietary accommodations</li>
